wiki.content: On “Cinderella,” Future reunites with Travis Scott for an uptempo trap banger that details the two detailing their drug use, expensive purchases, and the women they have had encounters with. The song was first previewed by Travis on the first night of “Road To Utopia,” a seven-night residency he had at the Zouk nightclub in Las Vegas on September 17, 2022. On February 11, 2023, SuicideIZA replied to a fan through direct message on Instagram, in which he revealed that it would appear on Future’s upcoming tenth studio album, and also stated that he engineered it.
